uprising is a 2001 war/drama television miniseries about the warsaw ghetto uprising . the film was directed by jon avnet and written by avnet and paul brickman . it was filmed in multiple locations , including bratislava , slovakia and innsbruck in tyrol , austria . this miniseries was first aired on the nbc television network over two consecutive nights in november 2001 . the miniseries 's soundtrack was the last film score composed by maurice jarre , and prominently features the work of max bruch , including his violin concerto no. 1 during the opening sequence .